=Statistics=

" they estimate 882 million works have been licensed under Creative Commons so far, and it's expected to exceed one billion next year. Also, as time has passed, more and more content creators have been sharing their work under licenses that allow for sharing, reuse, and the creation of derivative works such as videos and remixes."
